<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>CSS Properties Demo</title>
    <style>
        /* Text Properties */
        h1 {
            color: darkblue;
            font-size: 36px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        p {
            color: green;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        a {
            color: red;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* Background Properties */
        body {
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/150');
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
        }

        /* Box Model */
        .box {
            width: 300px;
            height: 150px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            border: 3px solid black;
            background-color: #ffe4b5;
        }

        /* Display & Position */
        .inline-box {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            margin: 10px;
            background-color: #ff7f50;
            position: relative;
            top: 10px;
        }

        /* Other Properties */
        .transparent-box {
            width: 200px;
            height: 100px;
            background-color: purple;
            opacity: 0.6;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin: 20px auto;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 100px;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>CSS Properties Demo</h1>

    <p>This paragraph demonstrates <strong>text properties</strong> like color, font-size, font-family, text-align, and text-decoration. <a href="#">This is a link</a>.</p>

    <div class="box">This is a box showing padding, margin, border, width, and height.</div>

    <div class="inline-box">Box 1</div>
    <div class="inline-box">Box 2</div>
    <div class="inline-box">Box 3</div>

    <div class="transparent-box">Hover Me!</div>
</body>
